'''''Exeter College Smoker''''' is a programme for a college concert, featuring  a cover illustration by [[J.R.R. Tolkien]].

The illustration has been reprinted in ''[[The Tolkien Family Album]]'' (1992), ''[[J.R.R. Tolkien: Life and Legend]]'' (1992),<ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=http://www.tolkienbooks.net/php/details.php?reference=11260|articlename=Exeter College Smoker. 1913|dated=|website=TB|accessed=13 February 2012}}</ref> and ''[[Tolkien at Exeter College]]'' (2014).
